      {
        "text": "A spawn drinking its master’s blood transforms into a True Vampire; drinking other vampires’ blood triggers frenzied hunger in spawn.",
        "source": "Drinking Vampire Blood"
      },
      {
        "text": "Free-willed mortals who drink vampire blood multiple times beyond their proficiency bonus risk addiction that manifests as exhaustion level 5 without another drink for days equal to PB.",
        "source": "Drinking Vampire Blood"
      },
      {
        "text": "Charmed mortals drinking their master’s blood become enthralled to Geas-like obedience for the charm’s duration.",
        "source": "Drinking Vampire Blood"
      },
      {
